=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Practice points</span><hr size=1> Hello, I was wondering if I could put my practice points left into Make Poison skill at my guild master, in order to level it  faster (especially the highest levels).<br>
<br>
In other words, I have 106 practices left, can I get my Make Poison skill up to 144 and put the 106 points to get to 250 ? ( Or is the guildmaster unable to teach me past lvl 200 ? )<br>
<br>
