<br>
The problems with your plan:<br>
<br>
1. Make poison is capped per level. You can't get to 250 until you're level 60. <br>
<br>
2. Guildmasters will only train you up to 200 in any skill.<br>
<br>
3. It takes a ton of cash.<br>
<br>
However there is an odd little way around the second problem - there is one guildmaster who will train you up to 250 in make poison, and possibly other things as well - our old friend Stanos.  Yes Stanos is a guildmaster and he will train you far above other guildmasters. So once you get above 200, go see Stanos and he'll be happy to take your money.<br>
<br>
Otherwise, yes you can do this. In fact many people do, especially at the higher skill levels.<br>
